  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.poster.avif?t=1747315168\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.webm?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.mp4?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as R0-L0 (a spherical robot from outer space) to <strong>roll</strong>, <strong>jump</strong>, and <strong>bounce</strong> through 6 colorful worlds to collect energy shards, so they can return home! Robo Rolo is a physics-based 3D collectathon platformer with fine-tuned, skill based movement that's fun to play, and even more fun to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.poster.avif?t=1747315168\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.webm?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.mp4?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to collecting energy shards, which unlock the way forward, you can collect sparks which allow you to upgrade your movement abilities even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/679b2c11a833d30af55244b7307e0022.avif?t=1747315168\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.poster.avif?t=1747315168\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.webm?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/ca5efa2390a90d870328141b3e30e9b3.mp4?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as R0-L0 (a spherical robot from outer space) to <strong>roll</strong>, <strong>jump</strong>, and <strong>bounce</strong> through 6 colorful worlds to collect energy shards, so they can return home! Robo Rolo is a physics-based 3D collectathon platformer with fine-tuned, skill based movement that's fun to play, and even more fun to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.poster.avif?t=1747315168\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.webm?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3563270/extras/a8b5061678ac0fa37904326ce18a8d3a.mp4?t=1747315168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to collecting energy shards, which unlock the way forward, you can collect sparks which allow you to upgrade your movement abilities even further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ct